room_title: Escape room "Oceans Royale" by The Lock Houston in Houston
room_address: 26797 Hanna Rd #5&6, Oak Ridge North, TX 77385
room_description: Participants must work together and take part in a casino vault heist of the ages! Of course, once you have the money and jewels, how quick can you get out? You gotta know when to hold em, know when to fold em and know when to escape the casino. Do you think you can avoid jail time?
